title: Data Centre Summit South
desc: Data Centre Summit South is a one-day conference focussed event taking place at the Barbican Exhibition Centre on the 10th of February 2016. Data Centre Summit will bring all of the industries thought leaders together in one place.? Data Centre Summit consists of? education, networking and debate, It will provide an open forum for delegates to be inspired by and learn from the best in the business. Other benefits of attending: Visit the exhibition of leading vendors
